  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个发布流程的旅程图，展示从本地开发到生产部署的完整自动化链路。主题就叫\"Release train and automation factor\"吧，重点突出不同阶段的参与角色和自动化程度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Release train and automation factor",
        "journey"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解为四个主要阶段：本地开发、代码审查、预发布环境和生产环境。每个阶段包含具体的活动和评分对吗？评分1-6代表什么含义？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Localhost development",
        "Review",
        "Staging",
        "Production"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，评分1-6表示自动化程度，6是完全自动化，1是手动操作。本地开发阶段开发者主要做Coding和Commiting，中间穿插Linting和Building这两个由git hook自动触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Coding",
        "Linting",
        "Building",
        "Commiting",
        "developer",
        "hook"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，本地开发部分我先画好。接下来Review阶段，Linting、Building、Deploying都由Pipeline自动执行，Probing需要manager、quality team和product team共同参与对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Review",
        "Linting",
        "Building",
        "Deploying",
        "Pipeline",
        "Probing",
        "manager",
        "quality team",
        "product team"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Review阶段Deploying是4分，因为还需要人工确认。Staging和Production的Pipeline自动化程度更高，Deploying都是6分，但Probing评分降到3分，因为验证方更多、流程更复杂。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Staging",
        "Production",
        "Deploying",
        "Probing",
        "Ops",
        "tech leads"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Staging的Probing我记录了Ops、tech leads、quality team、product team四方参与。Production的Probing角色略有不同，manager替换掉了product team，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Production",
        "Probing",
        "manager",
        "product team"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Production的Probing应该是Ops、tech leads、manager、quality team，product team在Staging参与后，生产环境主要由manager代表业务方确认。你刚才说的把product team换成manager是对的，但Staging那边product team要保留。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Production",
        "Staging",
        "Probing",
        "product team",
        "manager"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
